title: Discord Role for Loot Holders
body:
In keeping with the open and inclusive framework that Loot was built upon, the xLoot team feels that including Loot holders in our community is the best way forward. To help bridge that gap, we are proposing to create a verified role for Loot holders.  We believe it is in the best interest of the entire Lootverse to remain open and inclusive to all projects that follow this same core thesis.

This role would not entitle OG Looter holders to any special channels or benefits, and would not in any way take precedence over xLoot. The two projects should be viewed equally.  This role is simply to help those who hold Loot feel more included in our community, and a show of faith from the xLoot community that we are here to build bottom-up.
